snippet.title: KIRBY'S DREAM LAND (Game Boy) - Playthrough Longplay Gameplay
snippet.description:
Kirby's Dream Land Longplay / Playthrough / Gameplay for Game Boy.
It's better to play in black and white than in color. #kirby #dreamland #gameboy

0:00 Title Screen
0:21 Stage 1: Green Greens
3:26 Stage 2: Castle Lololo
8:05 Stage 3: Float Islands
13:04 Stage 4: Bubbly Clouds
19:47 Stage 5: Mt. Dedede
27:54 Ending

How to play Extra Game (Hard): Press up, A and Select on the tittle screen.

Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_FKcK36qxu0Oou7vFdoVlR
